item.title: 【UPSCALED】Lady Gaga - Poker Face [4K AI-Upscale | RTX HDR10]
item.description:
@SCANDAL thank you for the sauces. Even though, I'm using RealESR-Gx4 for upscaling from 480i to 1920p (MV resolution ratio is kinda whacky, and then some Sharpness Scaling it to 4K). In my speculation this MV have around 5-6 dynamic stops which is suck af, some part of it being blocky and AI can't even tell them apart and because of "smol" dynamic range, making RTX HDR conversion for it making some parts in the video being overexposure. Overall, I give this MV 4/10 points, and after upscale is 7/10.

Enjoy guys
